{"tid":1385124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仍然相信白警係正義之士嘅入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:57:15.000Z","uid":266482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b842369f903453d014d1104a4de55ebccb4be53","tid":1385124,"uid":266482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆，<br />\n仲係堅持自己係白警嘅警察，<br />\n只喺為左逗份糧養家嘅警察，<br />\n仲有有理想除暴安良嘅警察，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你哋其實心知肚明而家警隊有幾咁腐敗咖可。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n口口聲聲為咗以上原因，<br />\n但你地亦清楚知道每次衝突，<br />\n都因為你地嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">暴力濫權</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機會造成深遠傷害甚至傷亡；</span></span><br />\n都因為你地<span style=\"color: orange;\">肆意無理嘅拘捕</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機會毀咗人地一生前途，</span></span><br />\n<br />\n遠遠貴過你所逗嘅個份、<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">巿民納稅畀你</span>個份「人工」。<br />\n<br />\n自覺自己係白警嘅人，<br />\n你地做係唔可以只做「沈默的警察」，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你地係有能力幫大家咖！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n你地明明知道更多警察應付各種型勢嘅劇本（圖一），<br />\n可以畀你嘅良知幫你披露哩種無賴劇本，<br />\n點解咁遲先畀大家發現？<br />\n又或者有冇可能痴啲偷聽器係你嘅好同事身上，<br />\n幫下勢力不均嘅示威者？<br />\n又或者唔覺意射錯方向/浪費左子彈？<br />\n又或者搵多啲藉口放生被你同事拘捕嘅人？<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲咩走盞位，<br />\n相信睇唔過眼嘅你一定清楚更多。<br />\n<br />\n白警，<br />\n你可以唔洗辭職，<br />\n但你可以做更多。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔肯嘅話，</strong></span><br />\n只係說明你根本係一條狼狽為奸嘅警犬、黑警，<br />\n係哩個腐敗、無賴至極嘅團體生存，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁好心你就收皮，<br />\n唔好再自居白警，<br />\n你只係自欺欺人。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒有一個警察是無辜的。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCredit:<br />\n<br />\n(Mon Post狗入)【禍必及家人】正式宣布 由聽日起，會對班狗進行社會制裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378734\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378734</a><br />\n<br />\n同時，沒有一個警察的家人/伴侶是無辜的。<br />\n你嘅好生活將會受到更無微不至嘅照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因為你地太忙啦，<br />\n由其他人幫輕下你地嘅負擔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n圖：Facebook， 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9Kf9Qx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9Kf9Qx.png&h=e77d0bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkFrw3T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrkFrw3T.png&h=614dc83b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba9eadf78c827a2027202da2e8d1ba3df2ba7ef7","tid":1385124,"uid":99505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"沒有一個警察是無辜的。<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"e3d1042b4802b803d6ea2d692087e9c693b21bf6","tid":1385124,"uid":251111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:15:18.000Z","msg":"都成兩個月<br />\n有良心嘅一早唔撈<br />\n為份糧嘅埋堆變黑<br />\n點會仲有白警<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720d1932b02f9c98038eb8a0fabdf70a6b23ceaa","tid":1385124,"uid":266482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3d1042b4802b803d6ea2d692087e9c693b21bf6","tid":1385124,"uid":251111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:15:18.000Z","msg":"都成兩個月<br />\n有良心嘅一早唔撈<br />\n為份糧嘅埋堆變黑<br />\n點會仲有白警<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"唔撈係比較有良心，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家仲「忍辱負重」係入面做嘅，<br />\n逗份糧之餘，<br />\n都幫手平衡下勢力啦，</span><br />\n自己以為自己仲係白警嘅就唔好再自欺欺人，<br />\n反省下其實自己都係警渣。"}]}